CPHugN9HAKrYpeC6X65O5ZgqNATThPwkQKNJOcFe5HVBp4NwXD_Idoks6FGhNwEY4Pa3Dslk5UP-XsZOEmtfoVOgzzw2VQiyEc281pGFfaze5N1seyW9iYt/iw1Im72KqrbnaoVk3UfrliM39dPzNbo9/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="绿色日报"&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;订阅绿色日报&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;，每周六天在您的收件箱中获取免费气候新闻。&lt;/em&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 40px;"&gt;危险区域&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;根据气候影响实验室的分析，贫穷国家因高温死亡的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/IeTaYnzaLmzh9ySno2NpmFE7GoRNGQ1OcKvpee2m0OtRJJj6-D_BvyTwRr07NJgh45qCCim89cnvV-a-wgUBJ8rN7-b5zur-yntn0MOCN_K_KqbwQECt3sTcYzwJ0QWWURfiZOu3B-pgQRtUWGDGKjFg7fmfVk3PGk4F9KyMtJ5_lHkiS5klIyCx420QtqBczp8zQrEb_0TRVwh_ai5QhHlxZNz416dd6H8PD5lmqgewPdTyzU7rG7-TOyrq-uOJwmJqZhBJP_RIiJiVI1D4xbw2889Ye0mZugvajtRplZfk2laIsWr7LFO33fo-xZHHEjsD2wvuGbqb_epGwKeLTKQV-K8HvlcnbSCg_wPpdrsukjXvvMvFGhX_v0JMFPHVp48BFp8MFb4-cXo1A19Vq92drnEsRZYFUrJVAG3-HGoqdJ4FVJSAPU3DnvRi_FPHsMz85iF1DYcKDuo2nE6mw7sLGbdcxiX3fV1fGbDnAqFWgZ5TSFQiBdOyjg6XlmYzj5oyb3dnDDCpC6l67M-fjfDx0XWNt2Z5/2h6VooBOirJR_sn3DWGWOdY4DLPoex60/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="富国和穷国未来的高温危险截然不同"&gt;人数可能是富裕国家的十倍&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;这项研究于周三发表，旨在帮助城市和社区了解并应对气温上升所面临的危险。&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;与此同时，破纪录的热浪&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/LIjSBqHYjhHiUYLFMmEsqC7HEAIrUSM75hYMgcOezHMp4UFngnOTI1Eh-I3InMr_q5C-6kQZHce7OwQvPnNrYK-FaY1F_444C23GArKwdAgEHxGdP_dnJNKtKZ4bf2umTeTNe-b0SEiC-15IVzIvqTk-nWWzGKRBJ8hmCXE4Xenjk0FnnqF0wfCqfIMI-GLKbvrUMsb5vpT5DjC4rpToMvigm64UoDCXDWgiOtZN8F6jf9qWd6qmwnPRWE3jK06HddsduZKRSbrzFCKFjzmwUkAPnX_adFuY35hv-1pbLDXoermgg4xLMtRPFksuxa2dbo-ydLL7lhbONnBrWg3tyrXnL39EHXfIxFQ8XRbfydlv6lU_d0ot--pGfgtZEf02I8LwlkSbYMtdP